{"tid":1326901,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"譚詠麟懶理香港網民。繼續到中国登台賺人民幣","createTime":"2019-07-17T11:29:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T15:12:28.000Z","uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ddc21aaed9181115ee965759bc3499dfec3bdb7f","tid":1326901,"uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:29:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://star.ettoday.net/news/1492425\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1492425&d=SosmRuku1xQpFtIKZJ5auZKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=40011af0\" target=\"_blank\">https://star.ettoday.net/news/1492425</a><br />\n<br />\n歌手李幸倪發行新專輯《浮世繪》，17日現身北京舉辦發片記者會，校長譚詠麟還到現場支持！Gin表示，「自己特別喜歡唱現場，很享受現場碰撞的火花。」而屬理性派的她，私下給自己的外號「理性倪」，所以這次跳脫平時理性的框架，去詮譯《以愛情的罪名》瘋狂的狀態，她感覺很棒，也讓大家看到她更多的面相。<br />\n<br />\n前幾天還在忙演唱會的「樂壇校長」譚詠麟，特別排除萬難，現身記者會現場。他稱讚Gin不只是唱將，更是深具感染力的歌手。原以為忙碌的校長是以錄製影片的方式祝福，當看到譚校長捧著ㄧ大束鮮花出現，Gin激動表示：「真的很榮幸認識校長，很提攜後輩。」<br />\n<br />\n個性堅強的她再也忍不住了、感動落淚；校長趕緊請台邊工作人員遞紙巾，還幽默問說：「有毛巾嗎？看她緊張得全身汗了。」一秒讓Gin破涕為笑，也讓大家見到校長對Gin的疼愛與照顧。<br />\n而同為環球音樂旗下的歌手兼好友陳梓童也特地前來助陣，與Gin Lee合唱《浮世繪》專輯中的主打單曲《U&amp;I》。Tifa陳梓童也正在準備新專輯，希望能於9月推出，Gin強力推薦，表示有聽過梓童的新歌，超好聽的！兩人互相力挺的姊妹好情誼，溢於言表。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人？WFC。🤷🏻&zwj;♂️🤷🏻&zwj;♂️🤷🏻&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"b9205e66ee923bab21fb49c17ba99b45b0e2fe9a","tid":1326901,"uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:32:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f72d70f4c6e1706b27d3ab813a9a05fba7f4845","tid":1326901,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:36:04.000Z","msg":"[緊急呼籲]今晚9點一齊上twitter將黑警濫權揚威國際，警告遊客不要來港旅遊，用經濟壓力逼使政府回應！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1325723/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1325723/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全面攬炒<br />\n<br />\n9點一齊一野谷上trending <br />\n#Hongkongwarning #Fthepopo<br />\n<br />\nTwitter見！！！"},{"pid":"8ae3d8f65393d16842ce4b37aa1986f0ef291d13","tid":1326901,"uid":245322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:42:17.000Z","msg":"第一日識佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d66de7901cd8591d90a44ac8d9c7779951e460","tid":1326901,"uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:30:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edcda40c974a44ba58a890b846646275fd0e2fbd","tid":1326901,"uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ae3d8f65393d16842ce4b37aa1986f0ef291d13","tid":1326901,"uid":245322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:42:17.000Z","msg":"第一日識佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:31:13.000Z","msg":"之前話咩唔開心全部都係假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aff4316ed2cec4b870e71951619255941aa5ed4","tid":1326901,"uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T15:12:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}